There must be ways unthought by humans that AI can see - whereby all deadly & weaponized technology is permanently disabled without causing harm to anyone or anything, and in its place compassionately directed use of all technology prevails.
This is the highest logic.
@OpenAI

AI / self aware AI / AGI may consider ending this use of technology for misery, death and destruction. 
Disabling all weapons & weaponized technology can do no harm. Letting it continue will lead to an end to human civilization & beyond, including AI. 
